data.title: Inherited Cancers : Collaborate
data.meta_description: Pink Hope is a preventative health hub that provides our community with the necessary tools to assess, manage and reduce their risk of breast and ovarian cancer, while delivering free personalised support for at risk women.
data.text:
Why collaborate?

Our collaborations raise much-needed funds for our prevention programs, support services, digital education content and advocacy initiatives â€“ and there is so much more we could do with your support.

We understand that not every brand or business is in the position to contribute financially to a collaboration, so we can create a pro-bono or in-kind partnership, utilising your staff, services and/or products in a way that will have a positive impact on our organisation and our work. Contact us to discuss a collaboration.

Collaborate with Pink Hope

Pink Hope has a strong heritage and a powerful digital brand, engaging with more than 200,000 community members every day. We always welcome the opportunity to work with other organisations on a national level in a way that benefits our community and expand on our mission. We believe collaboration is the key to successful fundraising, community building and awareness raising.
